254
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:06,460
I'm wondering where this Xin Fa would be.

255
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:09,700
Would it be on Xiao Bai?

256
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:12,750
So, I just wanted to take the chance

257
00:18:12,750 --> 00:18:17,030
