258
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:23,700
Then, it's my fault.

259
00:18:23,700 --> 00:18:27,560
No, no, no. Of course, it's not!

260
00:18:27,560 --> 00:18:30,220
I know Brother are good to me.

261
00:18:30,220 --> 00:18:33,150
This was an idea that took a lot of thinking.

262
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:35,180
It was not easy to think of

263
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:38,670
