264
00:18:38,670 --> 00:18:41,150
Then, I will give you a few more days.

265
00:18:59,850 --> 00:19:01,680
Chief Leng!

266
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:06,040
- Chief Leng, I've kept you waiting. 
 - Chief Feng.

267
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:09,210
Chief Feng, did you send my regards to Chief Mang?

268
00:19:09,210 --> 00:19:12,290
I'm unaware of whether his health has taken a turn for the better or not.

269
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:14,720
Although Chief Mang is still ill and in bed,

270
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:18,950
