273
00:19:35,340 --> 00:19:39,110
But judging by your expression, I'm afraid I'm going to be disappointed.

274
00:19:39,110 --> 00:19:41,490
Chief Leng, you are ingenious.

275
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:45,810
This little girl, she insists that she's lost her memory and barely says a word.

276
00:19:45,810 --> 00:19:48,990
By my investigation, I'm afraid

277
00:19:48,990 --> 00:19:51,810
