278
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:57,130
It would be better for us to quickly take action and look for clues about the longevity fruit.

279
00:19:57,130 --> 00:20:00,950
Lest someone else seizes the opportunity and takes initiative before us.

280
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:06,250
Chief Feng, you have a great point.

281
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:38,750
There is moonlight shining before my bed!

282
00:20:38,750 --> 00:20:42,670
Indeed, the moonlight is beautiful tonight.

283
00:20:43,840 --> 00:20:46,130
This means...

284
00:20:52,750 --> 00:20:57,860
Young Master Xiao and Miss Chun Hua are really in a refined and elegant frame of mind.

285
00:21:05,290 --> 00:21:08,290
Young Master, do you still remember

286
00:21:08,290 --> 00:21:12,010
