287
00:21:13,540 --> 00:21:15,130
I remember.

288
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:19,240
The moon is bright today as it was at that time.

289
00:21:22,960 --> 00:21:25,170
Miss Feng is, indeed, a person who practices martial arts.

290
00:21:25,170 --> 00:21:28,800
On this great night, your voice is so loud like a large bell. I simply cannot sleep!

291
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,700
Sorry for disturbing Miss Chun Hua's rest.

292
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:33,520
My bad! My bad!

293
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:38,860
Miss Chun Hua, if you're tired, then you should pull out for the night and just go to bed early.

294
00:22:35,420 --> 00:22:38,270
Miss Chun Hua, I'm sorry.

295
00:22:47,420 --> 00:22:49,930
What a sin!

296
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:53,210
However, I like it.

297
00:22:56,660 --> 00:22:59,670
That vile Shangguan Qiu Yue...

298
00:23:20,360 --> 00:23:23,400
Little Chun Hua, how can you be so careless?

299
00:23:38,100 --> 00:23:40,640
Brother, why have you returned?

300
00:23:41,590 --> 00:23:44,000
If I did not return, how would I know

301
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:47,730
