302
00:23:51,690 --> 00:23:53,900
How can you act as if nothing has happened?

303
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:56,340
Every time, you randomly appear out of nowhere.

304
00:23:56,340 --> 00:23:59,330
Just now, you even peeped when I was taking a bath.

305
00:23:59,330 --> 00:24:03,560
You're my sister, not just any other person, and I also wasn't peeping.

306
00:24:03,560 --> 00:24:07,410
Besides, you've grown up with me since we were children.

307
00:24:07,410 --> 00:24:10,140
What part of your body have I not already seen before?

308
00:24:10,140 --> 00:24:14,040
Xiao Bai is insensitive and unromantic, but Older Brother is too demanding and shameless.

309
00:24:14,040 --> 00:24:17,190
This system is too crazy!

310
00:24:26,660 --> 00:24:29,710
Miss Chun Hua, is something wrong?

311
00:24:31,130 --> 00:24:33,780
In my room, I just saw

312
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:36,380
a really big rat.

313
00:24:36,380 --> 00:24:38,990
But now, everything is all right.

314
00:24:40,310 --> 00:24:44,350
The poem meeting will start early tomorrow, you should go to bed early as well.

315
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:54,830
Little Chun Hua,

316
00:24:54,830 --> 00:24:57,870
remember that you are a demon woman, not a fairy.

317
00:24:57,870 --> 00:25:01,320
I already told you last time, you're not allowed to use a beauty trap.

318
00:25:01,320 --> 00:25:04,620
- You would have embarrassed yourself. 
 - You...

319
00:25:09,820 --> 00:25:13,550
Your coming here this time is certainly because of the poem meeting tomorrow, isn't it?

320
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:16,620
I'm telling you, the righteous ones there will outnumber you.

321
00:25:16,620 --> 00:25:18,980
You won't have any advantages.

322
00:25:21,780 --> 00:25:24,720
You just need to look after yourself, Little Sister.

323
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:50,860
The weather is wonderful today. Master Fu, do you want to attend the poem meeting?

324
00:25:50,860 --> 00:25:53,270
Young Master, stop trying to confuse me!

325
00:26:16,820 --> 00:26:21,570
Presumably, everyone has heard the news about all the Xin Fa's that have been stolen.

326
00:26:21,570 --> 00:26:25,920
We must stay more alert to uphold the correct principles for the martial arts circles.

327
00:26:25,920 --> 00:26:27,480
The theme of today's poem meeting

328
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:31,540
is "The Theory of the Right Way".

329
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,950
[Halt Cloud Station]

330
00:26:33,950 --> 00:26:37,390
[The Theory of the Right Way]

331
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:42,060
"In life, we should be heroes among the living."

332
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:45,090
"In death, let us be heroes among the ghosts."

333
00:26:45,090 --> 00:26:48,040
Well said! Well said!

334
00:26:48,040 --> 00:26:52,610
Young Master Qin, don't you think this poem sounds a bit familiar?

335
00:26:52,610 --> 00:26:56,390
It seems like it's Li Qing Zhao's poem.

336
00:26:56,390 --> 00:26:58,350
It's my first time hearing it; thus, I really don't think so.

337
00:26:58,350 --> 00:27:01,320
Furthermore, who is Li Qing Zhao?

338
00:27:01,320 --> 00:27:04,530
A talented scholar like Qin Liu Feng doesn't know Li Qing Zhao?

339
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:07,480
Is it possible that the system set it up this way?

340
00:27:10,370 --> 00:27:12,270
Well, this is an easy matter.

341
00:27:12,270 --> 00:27:16,250
This year, the very best at the poem meeting will certainly be me!

342
00:27:16,910 --> 00:27:20,790
Shangguan Qiu Yue, don't think I dare not kill you.

343
00:27:20,790 --> 00:27:22,580
Come on, then!

344
00:27:32,850 --> 00:27:35,240
The formidable Master of the Chuanqi Sect.

345
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:38,880
How have you been reduced to being as weak as the righteous ones?

346
00:27:43,890 --> 00:27:45,910
Right now, three Xingzhu

347
00:27:45,910 --> 00:27:48,970
are lying in ambush about ten feet from me.

348
00:27:48,970 --> 00:27:51,870
Dozen of people are also waiting to act.

349
00:27:51,870 --> 00:27:54,130
Inside of your sleeves,

350
00:27:54,130 --> 00:27:57,030
there are still three viles of poison.

351
00:27:57,030 --> 00:28:01,040
As long as I take an action, I will be struck immediately.

352
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:03,950
Can you take care of me alone?

353
00:28:03,950 --> 00:28:07,300
Do you still need so many people to deal with me?

354
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:11,770
I still want to see how much you are afraid of death.

355
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:14,380
Cave Master is surely hilarious.

356
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:18,800
In this world, is there anyone who doesn’t want to live a long life?

357
00:28:19,800 --> 00:28:23,470
This poem by Miss Feng truly is filled with lofty sentiments and aspirations.

358
00:28:23,470 --> 00:28:26,650
Now, I’ll present my poem then.

359
00:28:27,850 --> 00:28:29,680
Great!

360
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:33,120
