365
00:28:54,110 --> 00:28:55,360
Excellent!

366
00:28:55,360 --> 00:28:58,640
“He does not care for his parents, let alone his children and wife.”

367
00:28:58,640 --> 00:29:00,650
Such a great way to return home!

368
00:29:00,650 --> 00:29:03,280
Young Master truly has the demeanor of a hero.

369
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:07,030
- Good poem! 
