370
00:29:10,020 --> 00:29:12,090
- Let me compose a poem. 
 - Miss, please!

371
00:29:12,090 --> 00:29:14,550
“Terrified at the beachhead of Huangkong Beach,

372
00:29:14,550 --> 00:29:18,000
lamenting my loneliness and helplessness in the Lingding Ocean."

373
00:29:18,540 --> 00:29:21,450
"There is nobody who doesn’t die in life,

374
00:29:21,450 --> 00:29:24,680
my loyalty to my country will be left in history.”

375
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:27,000
 Isn’t this Wen Tianxiang’s “Crossing the Lingding Ocean”? 

376
00:29:27,000 --> 00:29:29,450
 The system is surely lazy. 

377
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:35,010
“There is nobody who doesn’t die in life.”

378
00:29:35,010 --> 00:29:39,430
This Miss Leng is truly cold and heartless.

379
00:29:40,320 --> 00:29:43,890
“He does not care for his parents, let alone his children and wife.”

380
00:29:43,890 --> 00:29:46,960
Even though Young Master has the demeanor of a hero,

381
00:29:46,960 --> 00:29:49,340
when treating those around him,

382
00:29:49,340 --> 00:29:51,340
he is really indifferent.

383
00:29:52,330 --> 00:29:55,360
Indifferent? I’m also not from the Xiao family.

384
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:57,720
His being indifferent has nothing to do with me.

385
00:29:57,720 --> 00:30:00,510
I heard that you prayed

