392
00:30:19,810 --> 00:30:21,620
Just like the poem you have recited,

393
00:30:21,620 --> 00:30:24,990
sacrificing oneself in the name of loyalty is the right path.

394
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:28,250
I concur! Sacrificing oneself in the name of loyalty

395
00:30:28,250 --> 00:30:31,230
