418
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:47,790
When gathering, there is a sense of loyalty. After leaving, there are lingering sentiments.

419
00:31:47,790 --> 00:31:50,300
As the ancestors say, “a strong friendship has a deep sense of loyalty”.

420
00:31:50,300 --> 00:31:53,980
